OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fbecoming more focussed towards the
OL,7,Fnorth and west this evening and
OL,8,Fovernight, with some clear spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping across the region during
OL,10,Fthe early hours of the morning. Winds
OL,11,Fslowly easing.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FShowers are still likely in
OL,14,Fthe west on Friday, with more
OL,15,Fpersistent rain arriving here later.
OL,16,FVariable amounts of cloud elsewhere
OL,17,Fwith bright or sunny spells. Feeling
OL,18,Fcool for June.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
