OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FWindy
OL,6,Fat first on Saturday with coastal
OL,7,Fgales possible. Rain to start but
OL,8,Fclearing to brighter skies later.
OL,9,FDrier on Sunday though turning wet
OL,10,Fagain overnight and into Monday.
